{
  "stem": "24212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She felt like dancing, she was dancing around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Germans favored her, because Lily was entertainment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And last year I got hold of a book, I don't remember the name or title.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The first time somebody wrote a book about how these strange, slightly lucky people survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The clowns of the camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But finally, eventually, she went up the chimney.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you know, she survived for so long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then the Germans would give her the best of the soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Or sometimes even bring her, I don't know, a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Come on Lily.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, like you say, hey Fifi, and you whistle to your dog.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They say, hey Lily, come on, dance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she smiled, had ugly teeth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She's smiling.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So this is one inhabitant, one colleague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Across for me was Jadja, a Polish girl, Polish resistance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And once in a blue moon, when nobody else could hear us, we would exchange-- you know, I don't know how we found out about each other, by smelling, or how-- that what Jadja did, and what I did.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we had some similarities in, in our activities and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was Jadja.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then there was one girl who had a beautiful voice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean a God-given, beautiful, absolutely beautiful voice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she would sing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And her favorite song was 'Jealousy.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I learned at that time 'Jealousy,' I think, in about three languages.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because other people knew the same song.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Not English.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so I remember her singing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then there was a whole cooking group, very important.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I mean, seriously, very important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It sort of kept up morale.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
